    <item>
      <title>阿波罗开始交易蓝筹债券以打造私人信贷 ETF</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/apollo-starts-trading-blue-chip-debt-to-build-private-credit-etf</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 正将其新的私人信贷交易部门重点放在其发起的投资级债务上，并推出将其捆绑到交易所交易基金中的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/apollo-starts-trading-blue-chip-debt-to-build-private-credit-etf</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 15:50:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
