    <item>
      <title>勒庞预算言论导致法国债券风险降至两周低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/french-bonds-outperform-as-le-pen-revives-hopes-of-budget-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者希望法国议员能比许多投资者预期的更早就明年的预算达成协议，从而结束持续数月令市场承压的政治僵局，衡量法国债券风险的一项指标出现下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/french-bonds-outperform-as-le-pen-revives-hopes-of-budget-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 14:10:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗银行如何在澳大利亚大宗交易中损失 1700 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/how-citi-lost-17-million-on-biggest-aussie-block-trade-in-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团本周以低于竞争对手的价格赢得了澳大利亚七年来最大的大宗交易，但交易最终却以失败告终，导致这家美国银行的账面上有大量未售出的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/how-citi-lost-17-million-on-biggest-aussie-block-trade-in-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 03:39:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
